The '''''Star Hummer''''' was a [[Starship/Legends|ship]] owned by [[Joa Pqis]]. The ship was registered on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Vobos]] with registration number RN80-440330.

In [[16 ABY/Legends|16 ABY]], [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] tracked this ship as it passed the inner flight control buoys of the planet [[Teyr/Legends|Teyr]].

